name: "the man, the myth...Ricardus"
description:
Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.

"the man, the myth...Ricardus" is the fourth drop of the collection and makes reference to the esthetic and the character of @clokdhd , a great argentinian artist. We can see that now he seems to support warriors but he stills on the west coast.
